Class ProjectSearchCriteria

java.lang.Object
model.project.ProjectSearchCriteria
public class ProjectSearchCriteria extends Object
Represents the search criteria for filtering BTO project searches based on various factors such as neighbourhood, flat types, marital status, age range, and sorting preferences. This class allows users to specify the criteria they want to use when searching for available projects in the BTO system.
